Value.value: The demonic forces have pushed us back all the way here. We need to regain momentum so we can push back to our mountain fortifications and further...

You aren't the first adventurer nor will be the last we send. Go and raid the camp of the enemy and slay their current commander. Bring back their battle plans and we will reward you beyond your imagination.
I underestimated you mortal. You gave us aid in our time of need so we will return the favor. Take this.
I have nothing to say to you.
Go mortal! You have a noble task to complete.
